      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and taken care of, so it's totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It runs super smoothly and looks great, making it the perfect reliable daily driver for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. I've kept up with the maintenance, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
