    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example delivers exceptional throttle response and a linear power band culminating in an 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. Noteworthy mechanical upkeep includes a comprehensive VANOS system service and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the communicative steering feedback and balanced chassis dynamics synonymous with the M-division's peak engineering. A mechanically sound specimen ready for the canyon or the track.",
